<li><a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0735508739/ref=as_li_tf_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=collegebook-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=0735508739">Casenotes Legal Briefs: Evidence, Keyed to Mueller &amp; Kirkpatrick, 7th Edition</a><img style="border: none !important; margin: 0px !important;" alt="" src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=collegebook-20&amp;l=as2&amp;o=1&amp;a=0735508739" width="1" height="1" border="0" /></li>
